{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/10830", "repo": "rails", "body": "When using JSON columns in postgres it now throws `TypeError: no implicit conversion of Hash into String`.\r\n\r\nMy workaround:\r\n\r\n```\r\n  module JSON\r\n    def self.load(hash)\r\n      hash\r\n    end\r\n\r\n    def self.dump(hash)\r\n      ::JSON.dump(hash)\r\n    end\r\n  end\r\n\r\n  serialize :properties, JSON\r\n```\r\n", "_id": {"$oid": "5237db14bd3543c1510087dc"}, "issue_id": 10830, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/19377217", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/10830#issuecomment-19377217", "updated_at": "2013-06-13T07:54:30Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ebeigarts/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ebeigarts/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ebeigarts/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ebeigarts/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/ebeigarts", "login": "ebeigarts", "gravatar_id": "63bae10ff70c16aeeec4adb8f4c72f18", "html_url": "https://github.com/ebeigarts", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ebeigarts/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ebeigarts/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ebeigarts/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/63bae10ff70c16aeeec4adb8f4c72f18?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Ffb647ca6672b0930e9d00dc384d8b16f.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ebeigarts/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 8155, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ebeigarts/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2013-06-13T07:54:30Z", "id": 19377217, "owner": "rails"}
